#. <section class="sutta" id="sn56.37"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn56.37:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 56"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 56"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.37:0.2"
msgid "4. Sīsapāvanavagga"
msgstr "4. In a Rosewood Forest"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 37. Paṭhamasūriyasutta → suriyūpamasuttaṃ (bj) | suriyupamā 1 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn56.37:0.3"
msgid "37. Paṭhamasūriyasutta"
msgstr "37. The Simile of the Sun (1st)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
#. VAR: Sūriyassa → suriyassa (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "sn56.37:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Sūriyassa, bhikkhave, udayato etaṃ pubbaṅgamaṃ etaṃ pubbanimittaṃ, "
"yadidaṃ—aruṇuggaṃ."
msgstr "“Mendicants, the dawn is the forerunner and precursor of the sunrise."

msgctxt "sn56.37:1.2"
msgid ""
"Evameva kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno catunnaṃ ariyasaccānaṃ yathābhūtaṃ "
"abhisamayāya etaṃ pubbaṅgamaṃ etaṃ pubbanimittaṃ, yadidaṃ—sammādiṭṭhi."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, right view is the forerunner and precursor of truly "
"comprehending the four noble truths."

# See BB on variant
msgctxt "sn56.37:1.3"
msgid "Tassetaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno pāṭikaṅkhaṃ:"
msgstr "A mendicant with right view can expect to truly understand:"

msgctxt "sn56.37:1.4"
msgid ""
"‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānissati … pe … ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī "
"paṭipadā’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānissati."
msgstr ""
"‘This is suffering’ … ‘This is the origin of suffering’ … ‘This is the "
"cessation of suffering’ … ‘This is the practice that leads to the cessation "
"of suffering’."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.37:2.1"
msgid ""
"Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yogo karaṇīyo … pe … ‘ayaṃ "
"dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yogo karaṇīyo”ti."
msgstr "That’s why you should practice meditation …”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.37:2.2"
msgid "Sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""
